            <p class=3D"detaildesc">
              Ms Bokan is delighted to offer a 1 bedroom flat in a converte=
d four storey Grade II listed mid terrace house containing self-contained p=
rivate flats, situated in the New Cross area only 5 minutes walk from New c=
ross gate station (East London Line).<br>Benefiting from being newly refurb=
ished to a high standard. The apartment has 1 large double bedroom, open pl=
an living area, fitted kitchen with plenty of wall and base cabinets, newly=
 tiled floor, freshly painted walls, new worktops, gas hob/electric oven, f=
ridge freezer and washing machine and tiled bathroom with shower over the b=
ath tub. The apartment has recently undergone complete refurbishment includ=
ing full decoration and includes new furnishings. The flat comes with on st=
reet parking and is offered unfurnished or a double bed and a wardrobe coul=
d be provided if required.<br><br>.<br>Telegraph Hill Park is a 32 minute w=
alk to South Bermondsey, which is 1 stop to London Bridge. Also 10 minutes =
to Old Kent Road, where there are lots of buses to Elephant &amp; Castle fo=
r the underground, and also to Central London. Surrey Quays shopping centre=
 is a short drive away. Here you will find a Tesco Extra, Boots, Mothercare=
, BHS and other stores, plus an Odeon cinema and various restaurants. There=
 is also a Sainsbury's and a TK Maxx nearby in New Cross Gate.<br><br>
            </p>
